{"tid":1880764,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓紅出事！收明星捐款助抗疫　遭舉報13億巨款去向不明","createTime":"2020-02-15T05:53:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-15T10:15:15.000Z","uid":152123,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"89c5814502ac56d8d317bb38a5a4bee1c4b216d2","tid":1880764,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:53:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/RFKCaEh0tibit79H23H3pV_48ZU=/360x202/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/UVY6ISPBUBHZ5SI6EPFX35BFQQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FRFKCaEh0tibit79H23H3pV_48ZU%3D%2F360x202%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FUVY6ISPBUBHZ5SI6EPFX35BFQQ.jpg&h=0bfed7be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎持續肆虐，兩岸三地明星都掏腰包捐款盼助第一線人員抗疫，這次捐款管道多元，有中國紅十字會、武漢慈善總會、中華思源工程扶貧基金會、韓紅愛心慈善基金會等，其中由中國唱將韓紅率領的韓紅愛心慈善基金會吸引不少明星捐款，包括陳妍希、吳奇隆、任賢齊、王大陸、楊丞琳、吳克群等人都捐往此管道，疫區醫護也不斷回報有收到韓紅送來的物質，讓韓紅人氣跟著飆高，但韓紅並沒有公開明星捐款明細引發質疑，有網友向中國當局舉報，韓紅愛心慈善基金會自2013年以來有3億人民幣（約13億台幣）未依法向社會大眾公開相關訊息，而接到舉報的北京市民政局表示：「舉報已收到，高度重視，相關部門正在調查。」<br />\n<br />\n名為司馬3忌的微博網友列出4宗罪清算韓紅，一、基金會自注冊成立以來，歷年都未依法公布年度報告；二、去年8月前沒取得公開募款資格，之前長期非法採取鳥巢南廣場募捐、基金會官網募捐等多種募款方式；三、2013年以來對外投資累計超過3億人民幣，從未依法公開相關訊息；四、基金會設立的多個慈善項貝，執行時間長達多年，也未向大眾公布實施狀況。而韓紅方面尚未就此回應。<br />\n<br />\n但韓紅愛心慈善基金會多次深入疫區送物資，接收物資的單位都po文照感謝，她本人一度累垮生病，中國網友普遍肯定她抗疫表現，因此有人也質疑是因為別人眼紅韓紅才舉報她，但慈善活動最忌帳目不清，各項收支還待她說明白。（曾宛如／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"435a12b15a8609c691b44fdf0f0b516c8166c917","tid":1880764,"uid":23170,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T05:58:42.000Z","msg":"所以喺支那做好人係無好結果。等滅國滅黨滅全家啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b98ff8a18ee3366e6b7cfe4d1401ed4460d345a","tid":1880764,"uid":152123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:01:06.000Z","msg":"韓紅中左肺炎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1853990\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1853990</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4a4a1b6632300b7be19692fe84b625ae2590e42b","tid":1880764,"uid":69568,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"許志安d女出晒事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf7be1086ffec0171a98825f220559205c132fb","tid":1880764,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:02:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3f65aacb2edea1c4a464045902bf009bbc93d1","tid":1880764,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a4a1b6632300b7be19692fe84b625ae2590e42b","tid":1880764,"uid":69568,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"許志安d女出晒事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:05:19.000Z","msg":"點解老鼠很同隻肥野有路"},{"pid":"b2f19d5d8d7d9bdfe677b1c22e283e39e55599ed","tid":1880764,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a4a1b6632300b7be19692fe84b625ae2590e42b","tid":1880764,"uid":69568,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"許志安d女出晒事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:07:11.000Z","msg":"正想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a54864f4a0ca7821ed5146df91717f9882a4dba4","tid":1880764,"uid":240608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T08:11:06.000Z","msg":"大陸唔同香港。太易分化<br />\n講2講白變黑"},{